This mount did not work with my TV, even though the information indicated it would. I bought this wall mount for my 40-inch LED TV, which falls within the supported size range of 22"-55". However, after following the installation instructions carefully, I realized that the mount is not compatible with the VESA pattern of my TV. This was extremely disappointing as the product clearly states it supports VESA 400x400.

I tried adjusting the brackets and making other adaptations, but none of them worked. The mounting holes on my TV did not align with the pattern on the mount. It was quite frustrating, considering I had already purchased this mount based on the information provided.

Furthermore, the full motion and swivel articulating features mentioned in the product description didn't work as smoothly as I had hoped. The extension arm felt somewhat flimsy and lacked stability when I tried moving my TV around. It made me doubt the durability of the mount and whether it could hold the weight of my TV securely.

Thankfully, the package included an HDMI cable and a bubble level, which were nice additions. However, they couldn't compensate for the main issue of compatibility with my TV.

Overall, I cannot recommend the VideoSecu ML531BE TV Wall Mount based on my experience. If you have a TV with a different VESA pattern, it might work well for you, but make sure to double-check compatibility before purchasing.
